    - Pi-hole (admin):
        icon: /icons/pihole/logo.png
        href: https://pihole.srv/admin
        description: Bloqueo de publicidad + Resolución de DNS (Unbound)

    - n8n (admin):
        icon: si-n8n
        href: https://n8n.srv
        description: Automatizaciones del servidor

    - Firefly Importer (admin):
        icon: /icons/firefly-import/logo.svg
        href: https://firefly.import/token
        description: Importación de movimientos (solo admin)

    -  GitHub (repo servidores):
        icon: /icons/github/logo.webp
        href: https://github.com/Bludi90/servidores
        description: Código y scripts del servidor
